c: 12
v: 54
t: "masri amoytah Nabii Yuusuf kaal heenimik barih yanim kaah qaddowte waqdi kaa yoh baaha, inni malah caglisita marih num kaa abak iyye, tokkel Nabii Yuusuf kaal yemeete waqdi amoyti kaâ luk yaabeeh, diggah atu ta saaku Ni garil kaxxa arac litooh, kulliimih yaaminen num kinnito kaak iyye"